      <title>移民正在以令人惊讶的方式、不可预测的方式颠覆政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-17/how-migration-became-an-election-issue-for-south-africa-new-zealand-and-peru</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国选民越来越多地将移民作为他们的主要关注点。但这些来自五大洲的案例研究表明，世界各地的政府都在努力寻找解决方案——有些甚至加剧了问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-17/how-migration-became-an-election-issue-for-south-africa-new-zealand-and-peru</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
